
Changes in Version 0.8-99 (in development)

 o 

Changes in Version 0.8-92

 o argument negNA = TRUE to read.timeblob, can be specified in options.
   When importing, negative values are replaced with NA by default.

 o updated to use cor(use = "na.or.complete") in R >= 2.9.

 o can now resample timeseries to a shorter timestep (e.g. months to days).

Changes in Version 0.8-90

 o updated to work with new version of playwith package.

 o import from a general site list file format.

Changes in Version 0.8-87

 o fixed arealSubPolygons function for calculating Voronoi polygons
   (was inadvertently using base::intersect rather than gpclib::intercept).

 o fixed function grid.timeseries.plot.superpose when xlim not specified.

Changes in Version 0.8.76

 (not recorded)
